Details on the exact entrance to car park and exit locations can be found at www.theccd.ie/parking. Entrance to the car park is from 5pm onwards and a pre-booked ticket is valid from 5pm to midnight. Other car parks are available at: Connolly Station, the NCI, Dawson Street and Setanta place (off Nassau Street) or visit: www.aaroadwatch.ie
